body:
Because for some reason I still cannot connect to Avicus despite using the IP's, I'm bored. So, what's everyone's favourite Youtuber? It doesn't have to be about Minecraft, but anyone who you think is amazing on Youtube.

Mine is Markiplier- he is just so awesome xD. He is just an inspiration to me and I hope to be a nice character like him in the future.

What's yours?
